# T2 Skill Graph Context — loads on: igsl, skill, memory, node, health, evolve, hook

## IGSL v2 System
- Skill registry: ~/.igsl-skills/_registry_v2.yaml (13 nodes)
- Memory store: ~/.igsl-skills/memory/nodes.jsonl (44 seeded nodes)
- Health: EMA α=0.1, formula = applied_rate × completion_rate × (1 - 0.5 × fallback_rate)
- BM25 boost: score × (0.6 + 0.4 × health_score)
- Memory decay: weight × exp(-ln2 × age_days / half_life)

## Integration Bridges
1. skill-applied: bump memory weights, create ERR on failure
2. memory-to-skills: memory query → skill bundle suggestions
3. health-sync: write ERR nodes for low-health skills
4. session-context: token budget display
5. post-session: journal → memory nodes + skill evolutions + proposals

## Hook Chain
- SessionStart: session_start_v2.sh → additionalContext JSON
- PostToolUse: health_recorder.py (always exits 0)
- Stop: retrospective_v2.py (check stop_hook_active first)

## EvoGraph
- Modes: FIX, DERIVED, CAPTURED
- File: ~/.igsl-skills/_evograph.jsonl
